    <p style="margin-top: 2%;text-align: justify;">Kavya is your one-stop destination for skin and hair services that will leave you feeling confident, refreshed, and radiant. Our team of experienced beauty professionals is dedicated to helping you unlock your natural beauty, ensuring you look and feel your absolute best. Whether you're looking to rejuvenate your skin, enhance your hair's beauty, or indulge in a relaxing spa experience, we have the perfect solutions for you.</p>
   <h4>Our Skin Services:</h4>
   <ul style="text-align: justify;">
    <li><b>Facials for Radiant Skin:</b> Experience the ultimate in relaxation and skin rejuvenation with our customized facials. Our expert estheticians will assess your skin's unique needs and tailor treatment to help you achieve a glowing complexion. From hydrating facials to anti-ageing treatments, we have you covered.</li>
    <li><b>Chemical Peels:</b> Say goodbye to dull, tired skin and hello to a brighter, more youthful complexion with our chemical peel treatments. These exfoliating treatments will help reduce fine lines, acne scars, and sun damage, leaving your skin looking smoother and more vibrant.</li>
    <li><b>Microdermabrasion:</b> Renew your skin's texture and tone with our microdermabrasion services. This non-invasive treatment gently removes dead skin cells, helping to minimize fine lines, reduce acne scars, and enhance the overall health of your skin.</li>
    <li><b>Acne Treatments:</b> Our experienced estheticians will work with you to create a personalised acne treatment plan, targeting the root causes of breakouts and helping you achieve clear, blemish-free skin.</li>
   </ul>
   <h4>Our Hair Services:</h4>
   <ul style="text-align: justify;">
    <li><b>Haircuts and Styling:</b> Whether you're looking for a simple trim, a dramatic makeover, or a special style for an event, our talented hairstylists are here to make your hair dreams a reality.</li>
    <li><b>Hair Coloring:</b>From natural hues to bold, vivid shades, we offer a wide range of hair coloring options to help you express your unique style. Our experts will guide you in selecting the perfect shade and technique that complements your skin tone and personality.</li>
